{"tid":501662,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"我啲朋友大部分都買咗樓，佢哋話買咗樓先敢結婚喎","createTime":"2017-12-17T05:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T10:35:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":12,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e22c2898c39c76d72aa83dfa55945d448d840b35","tid":501662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:43:11.000Z","msg":"樓市大爆煲嗰時佢地就知味道，買樓買得咁開心吖娜，負資產就有你哋份"},{"pid":"246363d9c20c0cf9f398f5bb24d6d2888ddea995","tid":501662,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ae6887d90563a9a5bfaff08df662c0ac7ae75f3","tid":501662,"uid":45518,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"遲下啲人就會因為買咗樓而唔敢結婚"},{"pid":"2c1a911ae849d70733d0532a2fa7cd1fa895e8e6","tid":501662,"uid":104213,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T05:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/135548_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F135548_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=b07f838f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但又咁睇,負資產人地都叫做有樓,自住就冇問題,最多心痛,唔見幾百。結婚生仔一樣冇問題。<br />\n但冇樓就係冇樓"},{"pid":"471f5815029ab8c7cb5ae18d4c4281170f3bbc4d","tid":501662,"uid":77989,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:19:23.000Z","msg":"黑心到你 人地買樓關你撚事"},{"pid":"3df0955c4f0338ab7d4072f82a9b1ee4d3ddbe42","tid":501662,"uid":37612,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"跌唔跌你都買唔起架啦"},{"pid":"fc297e4069294f48b65cc20eed52b10806d4021c","tid":501662,"uid":37501,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"公屋仔發窮惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbeb9896adb5255bf1695cd4c33e3e2dd701bdb2","tid":501662,"uid":13645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T07:01:44.000Z","msg":"人地俾一半首期又話你知咩<br />\n跌5% d 人已經狗衝搶貨啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27dfe1be0522176ccaacdac88df5b4a23d8cf5b3","tid":501662,"uid":82717,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T07:16:46.000Z","msg":"有樓但有時都想睇樓爆，睇下人仆街，又可以入貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過未出手其實都係一齊仆街，差在會唔會蝕入肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過講真有左第一個單位，有部份人會敢買第二個，可以將第一間放租再買第二間，而未有樓嘅一直觀望唔敢買。當時自己買第一間屋時感覺係好似做咩人生大決定會猶豫不決，都拖左好幾年。後來我自己咁諗如果樓價唔升，供樓就當租樓，利息仲可以減稅，辛苦都係頭幾年因為收入會增加，而買錯左會損手蝕錢又未必蝕晒，供樓又唔使話供一世，未供完都可以賣。當時買第一單位嘅目的係自住，無諗咩投資，而買第二間時就會諗自住同埋有投資潛力，例如會睇埋生活配套交通同學區。第二間買左唔係好耐就升左兩百萬，升到我都覺得傻左。買樓好過賭大細，唔跌，你都贏。我識得有個uncle都係打工仔，買樓出租買買埋埋手上有廿個單位係唔同國家，唔知係咪每個都唔貴呢？如果我有多幾個單位收租都夠退休囉。"},{"pid":"2d55ca9c1a8d4dbcc95a5fac33c3c6b44103b8b7","tid":501662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81082786e54bb5530ab90c3a62d0b3cd432d5f75","tid":501662,"uid":42314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T10:04:27.000Z","msg":"買唔起既人唯一既寄望就係得呢樣 好可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3b2b20b6fb84d03fee3863eeed5318b378f0a9","tid":501662,"uid":159689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T10:18:09.000Z","msg":"每個月2皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將來會加人工,就算買樓都要供一世,但都要條女一齊供先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得如果本身屋企冇物業既話真係好難買到樓,<br />\n當然香港地實有大把後生仔有本事既靠自己買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca5b4756d9204d0dfa64a03b4de7f9cb2591680b","tid":501662,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"基本 無樓結咩婚咁唔穩定"},{"pid":"0e0960213f894e67ee076b58d9c9e3f5a372e8cc","tid":501662,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T10:50:41.000Z","msg":"sorry full pay jor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b827b7e1bb415d2624b6ab3cade9cc4c1eab64de","tid":501662,"uid":44513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:05:35.000Z","msg":"買樓結婚咁傻？<br />\n<br />\n有咩事離婚咪即刻要分身家？"},{"pid":"62d218fda6673302d40aa3642beee4927b531c06","tid":501662,"uid":22554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:10:38.000Z","msg":"其實結婚買樓都有少少迫不得已，　而家無左租務管制，　外來人口又不幾增加，　業主狂加租，　唔通兩年搬一次屋咩，　得一個人又話無乜所謂，　結左婚生埋仔就好難咁玩"},{"pid":"2d3894e2da4181b504cea8a08c530c0607b4eb8a","tid":501662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T14:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32581ef3cc09e272f0cea4d391fa259c4acef02d","tid":501662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T23:24:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf436b3179d51d3368d2a610c15717876014382","tid":501662,"uid":63212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T00:06:00.000Z","msg":"你係租？"},{"pid":"090c533f904cada45d1c502a9a8199e7d22d498a","tid":501662,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T00:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲下啲人就會因為買咗樓而唔敢結婚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16cf54e943c8a5e424d912cd554fb2f96a5639d","tid":501662,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T00:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公屋仔發窮惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c6500f3f33d471cf86631b2d6a638d221535b5","tid":501662,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T00:11:11.000Z","msg":"三年內睇下佢地有咩下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d242e9ba36ec6a013af9115589ed74263dc11616","tid":501662,"uid":141736,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T00:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓市大爆煲嗰時佢地就知味道，買樓買得咁開心吖娜，負資產就有你哋份</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己買唔到就咒9樓市爆，真係抵d人成日話港男冇用，真係唔撚抵幫"},{"pid":"0a33499da5632616a0108ea0e190d1e5d015aa10","tid":501662,"uid":6018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T00:19:15.000Z","msg":"幾年前買左樓，今年轉按，套左筆錢去買新車<br />\n仲要每月供款額一樣，你自己諗下代表咩"},{"pid":"6d68c233d23f2b104c49c36adc9cc37b594ec2f1","tid":501662,"uid":13897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T00:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買樓結婚咁傻？<br />\n<br />\n有咩事離婚咪即刻要分身家？</blockquote><br />\n我覺得有人會因為咁要離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}